nodes.text: Star Wars: Incredible Cross-Sections: The Prequel Trilogy

Star Wars: Incredible Cross-Sections: The Prequel Trilogy is a hardcover reference book published by Dorling Kindersley in 2012 as part of the Star Wars: The Complete Vehicle Cross-Sections and Blueprints box set. The text serves as a compendium of the previously published works Star Wars: Episode I Incredible Cross-Sections (1999), Star Wars: Attack of the Clones Incredible Cross-Sections (2002), and Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith Incredible Cross-Sections (2005), all of which were previously collected in Star Wars: Complete Cross-Sections (2007).
